dev_22.solution:
<think>
The question is to determine which film has the director who died earlier: Poker In Bed or The Machine To Kill Bad People. I need to find the directors of both films and their respective death years to compare.
</think>
<search>director of Poker In Bed</search>
<information>
Poker In Bed
Director: Oliver Hirschbiegel
</information>
<think>
I've found that the director of Poker In Bed is Oliver Hirschbiegel. Now I need to find his death year.
</think>
<search>death year of Oliver Hirschbiegel</search>
<information>
Oliver Hirschbiegel
Death year: 2021
</information>
<think>
Oliver Hirschbiegel died in 2021. Now I need to find the director and death year of The Machine To Kill Bad People.
</think>
<search>director of The Machine To Kill Bad People</search>
<information>
The Machine To Kill Bad People
Director: René Clément
</information>
<think>
I've found that the director of The Machine To Kill Bad People is René Clément. Now I need to find his death year.
</think>
<search>death year of René Clément</search>
<information>
René Clément
Death year: 1996
</information>
<think>
René Clément died in 1996, which is earlier than Oliver Hirschbiegel's death year of 2021. Therefore, the film with the director who died earlier is The Machine To Kill Bad People.
</think>
<answer>The Machine To Kill Bad People</answer>

artifacts.extracted_answer: The Machine To Kill Bad People
